        "Description": "Hoo boy... There\u0027s a Shagaru\r\nMagala goin\u0027 nuts in the Citadel.\r\nFlyin\u0027 objects resembling Qurio\r\nhave also been spotted. I don\u0027t\r\nknow if the two are linked, but\r\nneither problem can be ignored.\r\nGo investigate!",
